  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Protest in Yall against the arrest of empty-faced protestors",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A vigil was held in Jaffna on 29th Friday against the arrest of those involved in the empty face protest and to demand that it be stopped.",
        "The protest was carried out in front of the Jaffna District Secretariat under the arrangement of the North East Coordination Committee.",
        "During this protest, they carried banners with various slogans such as ``Don't Arrest, Don't Arrest, Don't Arrest, Stop, Stop Repression, Stop Repression.''"
      ],
